cz.cuni.mff.kocur.world

Class GridLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.world.GridLoader

  • public class GridLoader
extends Object
    This class should take file that contains navigation and height map of the game world and load the data into memory and represent them in a way that is usable later. It needs to load:
    • navigation map - blocked and traversable positions
    • height map - heights for every grid position
    Grid file looks like this: There are sections that are divided by section names (#heights, #navmap..). Each section should be parsed regarding its name.
    Author:
    Banzindun
